    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 inline-six. This high-revving power unit delivers linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline, benefiting from a recent valve clearance adjustment and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul to ensure optimal variable valve timing. The chassis remains taut, with a reinforced rear subframe to mitigate common structural fatigue. It features the Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission, providing crisp gear engagement and direct mechanical feedback. The suspension geometry is maintained with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, preserving its telepathic handling characteristics. While the exterior shows minor road patina consistent with its mileage, the drivetrain is in peak operational state, featuring a limited-slip differential that locks predictably under load. A superb driver\u2019s example for the purist seeking analog performance.",
